<lyrics>[V1]
 Okla moma haponakló,
 Chisʋs Chitokaka yokʋt
.    
     Ʋbanumpa hanta,
 Okla hʋsh moyuma hoka
 Chim auehinchi tok oka
.    
     Hʋsh haklo pullashke.

[V2]
 Hatak hʋsh moyuma hokʋt
 A luʋt ilbʋsha yoka
.    
     Hʋsh ilhkohonli ma,
 Chisʋs Chitokaka yokʋt
 &quot;Ont okchalinchi li hokma,
.    
     Okcha̱ya pullashke:

[V3]
 Hatak kʋna fehna hocha
 Ʋm antihi̱ya hokʋno
.    
     Shitilema la wa:&quot;
 Pim ahanchi fiehna hosh,
 Yakni paknaka ilʋppa
.    
     Ant anta tok oke.

[V4]
 Iti 'taiyukhʋna yoka
 Ahonʋhlʋt illi tuk osh,
.    
     Nitak tuchina ma
 Il okchalinchit tani cha,
 Ʋba aholitopa ya̱
.    
     Ont ahanta hoke.

[V5]
 Yohmi kʋt oklushi moma
 I̱ hullo fiehna hocha
.    
     Ilʋbshʋt illi tok.
 Yohmi kʋt oklushi moma
 Im anumpeshi atukma
.    
     Atohnohonchi tok.

[V6]
 Himak nitak fehna hoka,
 Chisʋs im anumpa pulla
.    
     Haklot il a̱shwʋshke:
 Yohmi kʋt ai okcha̱ya
 Pim anohoni tok oka,
.    
     Il aiokpanchashke.</lyrics>
<time_sig>8.8.6.D.</time_sig>
<title>Okla moma haponakló ƲIT37</title>
</song>